snippet.title: Sword: Depths of the Void OFFICIAL TEASER TRAILER (2022)
snippet.description:
The Sword Team and WorthyWorm proudly presents a new game to come (and it's our first!), Sword: Depths of the Void. Explore a forgotten world and fight for your destiny against the V01??D. Coming soon in 2023 - 2024.
